title: Sign in to the Construction Industry Scheme (CIS) online service

heading_context: Sign in to the Construction Industry Scheme (CIS) online service
chunks.html_content:
CIS contractors can use this service to:

  • file monthly returns
  • verify a subcontractor

heading_context: Sign in to the Construction Industry Scheme (CIS) online service
If you have problems signing in
chunks.html_content:
To sign in and use this service, you’ll need:

  • the Government Gateway user ID and password for your business tax account
  • to have added CIS to your business tax account

If you have not added CIS to your account, sign in on the HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) services page before doing this. You’ll be able to create sign in details if you do not have a user ID for a business tax account.

You can contact HMRC online services technical support.
